(100145, '黛米珠宝 心梦 9-10mm近正圆强光天然淡水珍珠项链正品女 送妈妈', '', 541, 530, 531, 541, '珠宝手表&amp;gt;时尚饰品&amp;gt;项链', 1, '掌门人店铺', 'N;', 'N;', 0, '', 0, '1_13895e698etb1qofx___0-item_pic.jpg', '', '<p><img alt=" height="238" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2wM2bbpXXXXXkXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg" width="790"></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2qWhJbVXXXXaPXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"></p> <p><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2DBcPcpXXXXcHXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2S4wKcpXXXXaRXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2dqgLcpXXXXaoXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-family: microsoft yahei;"><span style="color: #000000;"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2B_d7bpXXXXceXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2eiEKbXXXXXbmXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"></span></span></strong></p> <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 18.0px;"><strong><span><span style="background-color: #ffff00;">少量限量精选珠，已上线</span></span></strong></span></span></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span><span style="color: #000000;">对珠子饱满度要求比较高的亲，建议选择限量精选珠，珠形比普通版的要更饱满哦！</span></span></strong></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span><span style="color: #000000;">数量有限，不定期会补货上架！</span></span></strong></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #660000;"><span>--------</span><br> </span></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #660000;">珠形越大，视觉效果就越饱满哦~ 如想要佩戴效果显得大方大气的，建议选购9-10mm大小的珠子</span></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #660000;">10-11mm属于颗粒更加饱满，佩戴视觉效果非常强，特别大气型的，</span></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #660000;">而相比8-9mm的珠子，佩戴则显得秀气精致型哦~！</span></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: microsoft yahei;"><span style="color: #000000;"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2.dk0bXXXXXcGXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2nu7QbXXXXXaeXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2_7cObXXXXXbiXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.gif"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2soAKbXXXXXcUXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2A0gLbXXXXXb5XpXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2cAUFbXXXXXayXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2.AkGbXXXXXXCXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2KMkObXXXXXXuXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2x..NbXXXXXbBXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2ggkKbXXXXXXaXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2Pl7FbXXXXXaNXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2pYXMcVXXXXXaXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB26NgPbXXXXXaKXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2w1k4bXXXXXbaXXXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"></span></span></strong></p> <table border="0" width="790">  <tr> <td align="center" height="25" valign="middle"> <span style="font-size: 12.0px;">面对市场上五花八门的珍珠饰品类别，如何才能成为一名的聪明的"识珠人"呢？</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="25" valign="middle"> <span style="font-size: 12.0px;">近年来，主打"近正圆"标准的珍珠产品一夜之间成为无数商家推广和宣传的新亮点，</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="25" valign="middle"> <p><span style="font-size: 12.0px;">那么，"近正圆"珍珠的标准背后火爆的真相到底是什么？ 如何才能选择真正的"近正圆"珍珠及其饰品呢？</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="45" valign="bottom"> <span style="color: #cc0000;">"近正圆"是黛米2011年第一次在天猫提出的新的珍珠概念，近年在网上风靡起来，形成一个新标准，</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="30" valign="bottom"> <span style="color: #cc0000;">已经成为珍珠行业内一个最受推崇的亮点，</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="30" valign="bottom"> <span style="color: #cc0000;">对大部分人来说，即使完全不了解珍珠知识，但选购近正圆的珍珠却成为品质保证的基础。</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="30" valign="bottom"> <span style="color: #000000;">作为国内较早创立和首批进驻天猫的珍珠品牌，黛米为实现差异化品牌策略，特别提出要创新产品标准新概念，</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="30" valign="bottom"> <span style="color: #000000;">最终，"近正圆"成为珍珠规格被确立下来，</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="30" valign="bottom"> <p><span style="color: #000000;">随后在相关的珍珠产品描述上都主推了这一卖点，并成为了行业争相效仿的对象！</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="45" valign="bottom"> <span style="color: #000000;">然后很多商家，只模仿形，对近正圆珍珠真正的概念却并不研究，</span> </td> </tr> <tr> <td align="center" height="50" valign="middle"> <span style="color: #000000;">只一味打着近正圆的口号，珍珠品质却很低劣，从中牟取利益，黛米在此有义务提出"近正圆"珍珠真正的标准！</span> </td> </tr>  </table> <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: microsoft yahei;"><span style="color: #000000;"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2K8E2bXXXXXanXpXXXXXXXXXX_!!555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2HgEHbXXXXXXRXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2fZMRbXXXXXXEXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB29CwMbXXXXXb8XXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2KXEGbXXXXXazXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2fRgKbXXXXXc8XXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2dGgPbXXXXXbaXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2cgEIbXXXXXXmXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2B_3FbXXXXXarXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2JpUPbXXXXXaRXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2Q8ZIbXXXXXXhXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2gcQJbXXXXXXKXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2cF3LbXXXXXc2XXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/555253152/TB2C93ObXXXXXbfXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/555253152/TB2YK3RbXXXXXXBXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2U9sObXXXXXbmXXXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/555253152/TB2UgZlXVXXXXbIXpXXXXXXXXXX-555253152.jpg"><img align="absmiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/555253152/TB2Ny